      • customStringRequest

        public static void customStringRequest(android.content.Context context,
                                       int method,
                                       java.lang.String url,
                                       java.lang.String message,
                                       VolleyCallback callback)
        This custom Volley method uses Volley's StringRequest class and implements all methods in local VolleyCallback. This method uses context object to add request to the RequestController's RequestQueue.
        Parameters:
        context - Android app context
        method - Volley's HTTP method type GET, POST, PUT, DELETE
        url - URL to connect to
        message - a message to send
        callback - VolleyCallback object with overridden or implemented methods
